io.spine.server.bus

Interface MessageUnhandled

  • All Superinterfaces:
    io.spine.core.MessageRejection
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UnhandledRejectionException, UnsupportedCommandException, UnsupportedEventException, UnsupportedExternalMessageException

    @Internal
public interface MessageUnhandled
extends io.spine.core.MessageRejection
    An interface for the MessageRejection types which report an unhandled message being posted into a Bus.

    Except the methods declared in MessageRejection, this type is a marker interface.
